{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"506be757-5a9a-4de6-9a5c-cb52eaa7979d","content":"In ASP.NET Core, a **scope** is created automatically per HTTP request, so `AddScoped` gives you a fresh instance each request. **MAUI has no such mechanism** — there's only one scope for the entire app lifetime.\n\nThis means `AddScoped` behaves like `AddSingleton` in MAUI. Your `DbContext` is created once and reused forever, so tracked entities persist across navigations.\n\n**Fixes:**\n\n1. **Use `AddTransient`** — simplest option; new `DbContext` per injection:\n   ```csharp\n   builder.Services.AddTransient<MyDbContext>();\n   ```\n\n2. **Create scopes manually** via `IServiceScopeFactory`:\n   ```csharp\n   using var scope = scopeFactory.CreateScope();\n   var db = scope.ServiceProvider.GetRequiredService<MyDbContext>();\n   ```\n\n3. **Call `ChangeTracker.Clear()`** when navigating away, if you want to keep the single instance but reset tracking state.\n\nOption 1 is the most common approach for MAUI apps.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"16cb5904-6b31-4179-bce7-bf79f322feb3","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a common pitfall when moving from ASP.NET Core to .NET MAUI regarding dependency injection scoping — specifically why `AddScoped` behaves differently in MAUI than in ASP.NET Core.\n\nThis is a conceptual question I can answer directly without needing to search the codebase.\n\nIn ASP.NET Core, a \"scope\" is created per HTTP request, so `AddScoped` gives you a new instance per request. In MAUI, there's no concept of an HTTP request scope. By default, MAUI's DI container creates a single scope for the entire application lifetime. This means `AddScoped` effectively behaves like `AddSingleton` — you get the same DbContext instance for the entire app lifetime, which is why data persists across page navigations.\n\n\nTo work around this, you can switch to `AddTransient` for fresh instances each time, or manually create new scopes using `IServiceScopeFactory` when you need that isolation.","outputTokens":490,"requestId":"E840:29C906:266A3F9:2A91F68:69F94236"},"id":"9cec1517-9fa0-45f2-b8f9-8e048bc58c0d","timestamp":"2026-05-05T01:05:06.052Z","parentId":"8a60d3e2-82ad-4c78-bec5-fd2e28dfa56f"}
